        public Song(java.io.File song)
     throws java.io.IOException,
            NotMP3FileException
        Song constructor method that receives a mp3 file as parameter and starts the entire song metadata.
        Parameters:
        song - A mp3 file that represents the song to instance this class.
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException - if the file has not been found, deleted or moved to another location.
        NotMP3FileException - if the file delivered as parameter is not of mp3 type.
